      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 13:05:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关键通胀数据符合预期，美国国债上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/treasuries-advance-after-key-inflation-data-matches-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储青睐的通胀指标如经济学家预期的那样减速，美国国债价格上涨，增强了人们对今年开始降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/treasuries-advance-after-key-inflation-data-matches-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 12:44:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
